snippet.title: Guard Duty Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Guard Duty is now available on Windows, Mac and Linux:

https://store.steampowered.com/app/872750/Guard_Duty/

Guard Duty is a comedy adventure about love, loss and the end of the world. Experience an unforgettable story spanning across two radically different time periods.

Follow us on twitter: https://twitter.com/sickchickstudio
